<subSubSection pageId="54" pageNumber="812" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="54.[162,1380,828,2005]" pageId="54" pageNumber="812">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[171,408,1697,1730]" pageId="54" pageNumber="812">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Chinese Pipistrelle roosts in caves during the day, and has also been reported roosting in houses.
</paragraph>
