<subSubSection pageId="54" pageNumber="812" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="54.[162,1380,828,2005]" pageId="54" pageNumber="812">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[173,525,1815,1848]" pageId="54" pageNumber="812">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. The Chinese Pipistrelle is widespread and does not seem to face any major threats at present.
</paragraph>
